thread.title: Oil Giants Target Free Riders

author: Spencer Jakab
title: Oil Giants Target Free Riders
text:
The rules of the game are changing in the oil market.
Prices fell to their lowest in three weeks after reports that the agreement to curtail output by 1.8 million barrels a day between the Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries and non-member Russia was likely to end as soon as next month.
